# ğŸ“ Egrading API Wrapper

A lightweight **Python wrapper** for the **ENSAM Egrading platform**.
It handles **authentication, exam listing, exam data retrieval**, and even **automatic MCQ solving using ChatGPT**.

Built for students who like their grades served with an API. ğŸš€

---

## âœ¨ Features

* âœ… Secure login using ENSAM credentials
* ğŸ“‹ Fetch all available exams
* ğŸ“„ Get detailed data for a specific exam
* ğŸ¤– Auto-solve MCQs using ChatGPT
* ğŸ§  Supports **single & multiple correct answers**
* ğŸª Automatic handling of **access & refresh tokens**
* âš¡ Fast, lightweight, and hackable

